These requests for a preliminary ruling concern the interpretation of Fourth Council Directive 78/660/EEC of 25 July 1978 based on Article [50(2)(g) TFEU] on the annual accounts of certain types of companies (
OJ 1978 L 222, p. 11
), as amended by Directive 2003/51/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council of 18 June 2003 (
OJ 2003 L 178, p. 16
) (‘Directive 78/660’).
